CVS/Metrics
===========

    CVS::Metrics - Utilities for process cvs log

    This module supplies 6 utilities :
      - cvs_activity
      - cvs_energy
      - cvs_tklog (Tk)
      - cvs_wxlog (wxWindows)
      - cvs_current
      - cvs_revbytag
    and 2 CGI scripts :
      - cgi_cvs_evolq
      - cgi_cvs_evolr

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  GD, GD::Graph, Parse::RecDescent, Chart::Plot::Canvas

